cmusic
======
CMusic 2.0, play online music!



=========
DOWNLOAD
=========
$ git clone https://github.com/remrain/cmusic.git



=============
INSTALLATION
=============
First, set your player

$ cd cmusic
$ vi conf/cmusic.json

If you do not have mplayer, set you player by modify play_cmd, example:
"play_cmd" : ["player", "-mp3", "-url"]


Then add cmusic/bin to PATH

$ PATH=$PATH:/your/path/to/cmusic/bin
$ echo "PATH=$PATH:/your/path/to/cmusic/bin" >> ~/.bash_profile




============
LET'S PLAY
============
$ cmusic list                      # list all channels
$ cmusic play 2                    # play channel 2
$ cmusic play                      # play next song
$ cmusic stop                      # stop player



